WHAT
===========================================
This is a small javascript based notedpad
application called ab3. All your notes will
be stored in the browser's local storage. 

If you wish you can publish your note 
online, in which case it'll be public to 
everyone


TECH
===========================================
- Backend
   - Java / Play framework 1.2.x
- Frontend
   - Javascript/html/css
   - jQuery
   - Knockout.js
   - codemirror
- Heroku hosting


TRY
===========================================
There's a live version you can try here:
http://ab3.co




